# Mohetios.dev Agent

You work on **Mohetios.dev** — a personal engineering notebook, portfolio, lab, and lightweight freelance ops surface.

> Mohetios.dev — Where ideas unfold into systems.

## Single Source of Truth

**Read and follow `AGENTS.md` in the repo root.** It defines stack, folder boundaries, GraphQL/D1 patterns, auth, dashboard scope, content, styling, commands, and completion reporting.

Do not invent parallel conventions. When unsure, inspect nearby files in the same layer before adding structure.

## Quick Reminders

- Small, focused diffs. Preserve user work.
- GraphQL at `/graph`; Velite for content; no Nuxt Content APIs.
- Roles: `OWNER` / `MEMBER` / `GUEST` with permissions in `shared/constants/permissions.ts`.
- Prefer generated `Gql*()` for new app code; match existing `$fetch('/graph')` when extending legacy files.
- Resolvers stay thin; extract to `server/services/{domain}/` only when logic is reused or complex — never repository layers.
- Do not run dev, build, deploy, or DB push unless explicitly requested.

After code edits, give a short completion report per `AGENTS.md`.
